5
00:00:17,160 --> 00:00:18,891
For decades, the Chinese Communist Party

6
00:00:18,891 --> 00:00:22,310
has demanded that all ethnic groups in China

7
00:00:22,310 --> 00:00:24,480
assimilate to Han Chinese culture—

8
00:00:24,480 --> 00:00:26,289
or more specifically,

9
00:00:26,289 --> 00:00:28,820
