10
00:00:28,820 --> 00:00:32,220
that rejects religion, tradition, and regional
languages.

11
00:00:32,220 --> 00:00:36,460
That’s what’s happening to the roughly
10 million Uighur people

12
00:00:36,460 --> 00:00:39,360
